precis:
Enactment of the VETERANS REVIEW AND APPEAL BOARD REGULATIONS which set out
the procedural rules for applying for and deciding upon reviews, appeals
and questions of interpretation, for reconsidering appeal decisions, for
receiving medical evidence, and for informing applicants and appellants
about decisions and their rights of appeal.
